<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 12:14:50 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列法院暂停本-格维尔晋升因对抗议者施暴而接受调查的警官</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/court-halts-ben-gvirs-promotion-of-police-officer-accused-of-violence-against-protesters/00000191-c703-de0a-afd5-df4be6440000</link><description>法官裁定，梅厄·苏伊萨的晋升“明显偏离了警方的法律和专业审查程序”。 Suissa 目前正在接受犯罪调查，其中包括向 2023 年反司法改革抗议者投掷眩晕手榴弹</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 11:40:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/court-halts-ben-gvirs-promotion-of-police-officer-accused-of-violence-against-protesters/00000191-c703-de0a-afd5-df4be6440000</guid></item><item><title>定居者摧毁了他们的西岸村庄，以色列禁止他们重建它</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-09-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/settlers-destroyed-their-west-bank-village-israel-forbids-them-from-rebuilding-it/00000191-c24c-de0a-afd5-da4c24d10000</link><description>战争开始时，一个巴勒斯坦社区因担心定居者袭击而放弃了位于南希伯伦山的祖传村庄。以色列法院的裁决允许他们返回，但定居者已经摧毁了他们的大部分房屋。现在军政府不让他们重建</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 11:18:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-09-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/settlers-destroyed-their-west-bank-village-israel-forbids-them-from-rebuilding-it/00000191-c24c-de0a-afd5-da4c24d10000</guid></item><item><title>随着加沙停火和人质协议濒临崩溃，一个不太可能的步骤可能会使其取得成果</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-cease-fire-deal-on-brink-of-collapse-one-unlikely-step-could-bring-it-to-fruition/00000191-c670-df27-a9b9-fffa76690000</link><description>美国将提出最终的“要么接受要么放弃”的提案，这将迫使内塔尼亚胡和哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔决定是否放弃骄傲并妥协。拒绝将大大增加发生地区战争的可能性</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:58:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/as-gaza-cease-fire-deal-on-brink-of-collapse-one-unlikely-step-could-bring-it-to-fruition/00000191-c670-df27-a9b9-fffa76690000</guid></item><item><title>面对严峻的经济危机，伊朗越来越将加沙战争视为负担</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/faced-with-a-dire-economic-crisis-iran-increasingly-views-the-war-in-gaza-as-a-burden/00000191-c62d-d7cf-a59d-c6ed18320000</link><description>伊朗担心，其与其代理人针对以色列制定的“反应方程式”政策可能会适得其反，将其拖入地区冲突，从而加剧其本已严峻的经济挑战，并阻碍新政府寻求复兴的努力</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:41:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/faced-with-a-dire-economic-crisis-iran-increasingly-views-the-war-in-gaza-as-a-burden/00000191-c62d-d7cf-a59d-c6ed18320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列计划在联合国教科文组织世界遗产地建立新的西岸定居点，这违反了承诺</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-plans-new-w-bank-settlement-at-unesco-world-heritage-site-in-breach-of-commitments/00000191-c669-d76a-a5f1-f66b2f4e0000</link><description>2014年，应巴勒斯坦权力机构的要求，联合国教科文组织将巴蒂尔古代梯田列为世界遗产。尽管以色列七年前退出联合国教科文组织，但它从未放弃在该公约上的签署和承诺</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 09:09:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-plans-new-w-bank-settlement-at-unesco-world-heritage-site-in-breach-of-commitments/00000191-c669-d76a-a5f1-f66b2f4e0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯发布被谋杀的以色列裔美国人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的囚禁视频</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/hamas-publishes-captivity-video-of-murdered-israeli-american-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin/00000191-c5e1-d86a-a5d7-f5f912400000</link><description>赫什在视频中说，他在加沙幸存下来，几乎没有得到任何医疗护理，而且“不记得上次看到太阳或呼吸新鲜空气是什么时候了。”他的父母表示，这段视频必须立即给世界敲响警钟，要求他们采取行动，确保剩余人质获释。</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 06:41:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/hamas-publishes-captivity-video-of-murdered-israeli-american-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin/00000191-c5e1-d86a-a5d7-f5f912400000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的信息直接针对哈马斯领导人辛瓦尔：“别打扰”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-message-is-aimed-squarely-at-sinwar-dont-bother/00000191-c334-d3f8-adf5-df7e83a90000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡知道人质协议意味着他没有联盟 ■ 在所有人中，他未能采取必要措施来对抗伊朗核项目 ■ 约旦河西岸爆炸物的使用正在增加</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 03:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-message-is-aimed-squarely-at-sinwar-dont-bother/00000191-c334-d3f8-adf5-df7e83a90000</guid></item><item><title>有组织的骚扰不会阻止唯一关心人质的以色列部长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/organized-harassment-wont-deter-the-only-israeli-minister-who-cares-about-the-hostages/00000191-c3a7-de0a-afd5-dbef91020000</link><description>本周针对国防部长约夫·加兰特的骚扰活动愈演愈烈，但他无意辞职 ■ 本周很可能会被铭记为内塔尼亚胡放弃人质的一周 ■ 本-格维尔和斯莫特里奇不能被威胁吓倒包括西岸的区域战争；相反，他们渴望世界末日</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 03:00:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/organized-harassment-wont-deter-the-only-israeli-minister-who-cares-about-the-hostages/00000191-c3a7-de0a-afd5-dbef91020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军：两枚反坦克导弹袭击以色列北部；黎巴嫩报告以色列袭击南部地区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-live/hamas-publishes-captivity-video-of-murdered-israeli-american-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin/00000191-c4f4-d7cf-a59d-c6f5292a0000</link><description>黎巴嫩媒体报道以色列对黎巴嫩南部的袭击 ■ 定居者在拉马拉地区的两个巴勒斯坦村庄放火焚烧车辆并破坏建筑物 ■ 联合国警告加沙地带的人道主义局势“超出灾难性” ■ 巴勒斯坦通讯社：以色列国防军从约旦河西岸城市杰宁撤军, Tul Karm 手术 10 天后</description><pubDate>Fri, 06 Sep 2024 01:46:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-live/hamas-publishes-captivity-video-of-murdered-israeli-american-hostage-hersh-goldberg-polin/00000191-c4f4-d7cf-a59d-c6f5292a0000</guid></item><item><title>尽管家人一再呼吁不要政治，但共和党人为袭击拜登的人质辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/gop-defends-attacking-biden-on-hostages-despite-families-repeated-calls-for-no-politics/00000191-c47a-dd1b-a7db-f7fe07220001</link><description>共和党议员利用共和党犹太联盟的年度会议明确指责拜登和哈里斯授权哈马斯，但未能采取足够措施营救人质</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 23:38:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/gop-defends-attacking-biden-on-hostages-despite-families-repeated-calls-for-no-politics/00000191-c47a-dd1b-a7db-f7fe07220001</guid></item><item><title>蒂姆·沃尔兹：内塔尼亚胡是时候开始朝着两国解决方案的方向迈进了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/tim-walz-time-for-netanyahu-to-start-moving-in-the-direction-of-a-two-state-solution/00000191-c44a-d86a-a5d7-f55a67470000</link><description>这是哈里斯或她的竞选搭档首次直接点名以色列总理的评论</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 22:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/tim-walz-time-for-netanyahu-to-start-moving-in-the-direction-of-a-two-state-solution/00000191-c44a-d86a-a5d7-f55a67470000</guid></item><item><title>以色列海牙法官：政权政变抗议者“厌恶米兹拉希姆，害怕正统派”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-judge-at-icc-regime-coup-protesters-disgusted-by-mizrahim-afraid-of-haredim/00000191-c40d-d104-a991-cf9f26ad0000</link><description>担任国际法院以色列专案法官的罗恩·夏皮拉教授表示，那些反对政府司法改革的示威者“真正担心这个国家被从他们手中偷走了”</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 22:02:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article/.premium/israels-judge-at-icc-regime-coup-protesters-disgusted-by-mizrahim-afraid-of-haredim/00000191-c40d-d104-a991-cf9f26ad0000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日效应：以色列人离开以色列，散居海外的犹太人取代了他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-october-7-effect-the-israelis-leaving-israel-and-the-diaspora-jews-replacing-them/00000191-b6b7-d13c-a39b-bebff9830000</link><description>自 10 月 7 日以来，由于反犹太主义、反犹太复国主义、与以色列的团结、对战争和民主崩溃的恐惧，或者仅仅是高昂的生活成本，数以万计的犹太人离开家园，往返于以色列。 21世纪第三个十年又回到漂泊的生活？</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 21:20:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-06/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-october-7-effect-the-israelis-leaving-israel-and-the-diaspora-jews-replacing-them/00000191-b6b7-d13c-a39b-bebff9830000</guid></item><item><title>“剩下的就是费城”：以色列各地数千人抗议加沙人质释放协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-for-gaza-hostage-release-deal/00000191-c36c-de0a-afd5-db6c4e3d0000</link><description>数以千计的以色列人在特拉维夫、耶路撒冷、海法和其他城市举行示威，要求达成释放人质协议，内塔尼亚胡批评内塔尼亚胡数天内第二次混淆了 10 月 7 日哈马斯袭击的日期</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 20:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/thousands-protest-across-israel-for-gaza-hostage-release-deal/00000191-c36c-de0a-afd5-db6c4e3d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方调查西岸巴勒斯坦被拘留者在监狱中遭受性虐待的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-investigates-palestinian-detainees-allegation-of-sexual-abuse-in-prison/00000191-c27e-d870-a59d-e67fb2200000</link><description>西岸的一名巴勒斯坦居民声称，自加沙战争爆发以来，以色列监狱工作人员多次对他进行性虐待和身体虐待，并且无视他的医疗请求</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 19:53:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-police-investigates-palestinian-detainees-allegation-of-sexual-abuse-in-prison/00000191-c27e-d870-a59d-e67fb2200000</guid></item><item><title>拜登，如果你真的想了解内塔尼亚胡，听听他用希伯来语说的话</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/biden-if-you-really-want-to-understand-netanyahu-listen-to-what-he-says-in-hebrew/00000191-c1f2-db84-a3bd-ebfee9380000</link><description>对于总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡来说，加沙的费城路线现在是摆脱任何可能的停火和人质协议的最快途径。美国政府会知道，如果它在过去几个月里更加关注他的希伯来语演讲</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 19:11:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/biden-if-you-really-want-to-understand-netanyahu-listen-to-what-he-says-in-hebrew/00000191-c1f2-db84-a3bd-ebfee9380000</guid></item><item><title>像乌克兰一样：真主党开始用 FPV 赛车无人机攻击以色列军队</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/like-ukraine-hezbollah-begins-attacking-israeli-forces-with-fpv-racing-drones/00000191-c338-d870-a59d-e77bec490000</link><description>乌克兰战场上最致命的武器之一最近出现在真主党与以色列的冲突中，而且极其难以拦截：第一人称视角无人机，可以让飞行员从飞机的角度观察</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 18:41:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/like-ukraine-hezbollah-begins-attacking-israeli-forces-with-fpv-racing-drones/00000191-c338-d870-a59d-e77bec490000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的地图显示了以色列“从河流到海洋”。这绝非偶然</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-05/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-map-shows-israel-from-the-river-to-the-sea-its-no-accident/00000191-c2a8-d09f-ab91-debc90e60000</link><description>在总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的“费城”演讲中，还有一个很少有人注意到的信息，尽管它根本没有隐藏</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 18:13:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-09-05/ty-article/.highlight/netanyahus-map-shows-israel-from-the-river-to-the-sea-its-no-accident/00000191-c2a8-d09f-ab91-debc90e60000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯以色列记者因悲痛的被杀人质遭受种族主义袭击而向警方投诉</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-journalist-files-police-complaint-following-torrent-of-racist-attacks/00000191-c2a1-d09f-ab91-debd319f0000</link><description>以色列阿拉伯电视主持人露西·阿哈里什（Lucy Aharish）充满激情的独白哀悼在加沙被谋杀的六名人质在网上被分享后，这位记者在社交媒体和她的个人手机上收到了大量种族主义攻击</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:57:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/arab-israeli-journalist-files-police-complaint-following-torrent-of-racist-attacks/00000191-c2a1-d09f-ab91-debd319f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列、美国、英国和欧洲国家签署具有里程碑意义的国际人工智能条约</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-u-s-britain-and-european-countries-sign-landmark-international-ai-treaty/00000191-c2cd-d3f8-adf5-deefe7660000</link><description>《人工智能公约》要求公司保护人权和民主制度，同时保持透明度、隐私和平等，并将主要适用于公共部门</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 17:45:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/2024-09-05/ty-article/.premium/israel-u-s-britain-and-european-countries-sign-landmark-international-ai-treaty/00000191-c2cd-d3f8-adf5-deefe7660000</guid></item></channel></rss>